						<div class="postbody">I think the -1 was for the pre-render scanline, in which case 0-239 would be the visible picture, 240 would be the post-render scanline, and 241-260 would be VBlank, so the for should be <tt style="margin-left: 2px; margin-right: 2px; padding:3px; background-color: #3355aa; color: white;">for&#40;int i = -1; i &lt; 261; i++&#41;</tt>. I think that numbering an scanline as -1 is a bit confusing though.</div>

